*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.psd binary
*.tga binary
*.tif binary
*.tiff binary
*.bmp binary
*.exr binary
*.wav binary
*.mp3 binary
*.ogg binary
*.aif binary
